## Data Flow Between Files

```
LightController          light_control.py
    в”Ӯ TrafficSignals
    в–ј
vehicle_step()           step.py  вҶҗв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ Vehicle.decide_move()   vehicle.py
    в”Ӯ dict[car_idвҶ’CarState]                          вҶ‘
    в”Ӯ                                         Fleet + routing            fleet.py, routing.py
    в–ј
evaluate_checks()        checks.py  (i-group)
    в”Ӯ ChecksReport
    в–ј
CumulativeMetrics        simulation.py
    в”Ӯ
    в–ј
stopped_cars_per_intersection()  congestion.py
    в”Ӯ congestion_map
    в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв–¶  vehicle_step() (next iteration)
```

